<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <style>
      /* Add your custom CSS styles here */
      body {
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #333333;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      p {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      a {
        color: #007bff;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 4px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <h1>Contact Form Submission</h1>

    <p>Dear Admin,</p>

    <p>You have received a new message from a user:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Name: <%= @contact.name %></li>
      <li>Email: <%= @contact.email %></li>
      <li>Message: <%= @contact.message %></li>
    </ul>

    <p>Please follow up with the user as soon as possible.</p>

    <p>Best regards,</p>

    <p>The Beta Tech Team</p>

  </body>
</html>
